<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>R & F Construction</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>

<body>

<a class="skip-link" href="#main-content">Skip to Main Content</a>

<header>
    <h1>R & F Construction</h1>
    <p>Building Quality. Creating Trust.</p>

    <nav aria-label="Main Navigation">
        <ul>
            <li><a href="#home">Home</a></li>
            <li><a href="#services">Services</a></li>
            <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
            <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>
</header>

<main id="main-content">

<section id="home" class="hero">
    <h2>Welcome to R & F Construction</h2>

    <p>
        We specialize in residential and commercial construction,
        remodeling, renovations, and custom building solutions.
        Our mission is to deliver quality craftsmanship with
        dependable service.
    </p>

    <button id="learnMoreBtn">Learn More</button>
</section>

<section id="services">

    <h2>Our Services</h2>

    <div class="card">
        <h3>Residential Construction</h3>
        <p>
            New homes, additions, garages, and complete remodeling.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <h3>Commercial Construction</h3>
        <p>
            Office renovations, retail spaces, and commercial buildings.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <h3>Roofing & Exterior</h3>
        <p>
            Roofing, siding, windows, decks, and outdoor improvements.
        </p>
    </div>

</section>

<section id="about">

    <h2>About Us</h2>

    <p>
        R & F Construction is committed to providing dependable,
        affordable, and high-quality construction services. Our experienced
        team works closely with every client to ensure each project is
        completed safely, on time, and within budget.
    </p>

</section>

<section id="contact">

    <h2>Contact Us</h2>

    <form>

        <label for="name">Name</label>
        <input
            type="text"
            id="name"
            name="name"
            required>

        <label for="email">Email</label>
        <input
            type="email"
            id="email"
            name="email"
            required>

        <label for="message">Message</label>

        <textarea
            id="message"
            name="message"
            rows="5"
            required></textarea>

        <button type="submit">Send Message</button>

    </form>

</section>

</main>

<footer>
    <p>&copy; 2026 R & F Construction. All Rights Reserved.</p>
</footer>

<script src="script.js"></script>

</body>
</html>
